Klasse CalendarEntryRepository

java.lang.Object
de.fherfurt.lat.storage.data.repositories.CalendarEntryRepository
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
ICalendarEntryRepository
public class CalendarEntryRepository extends Object implements ICalendarEntryRepository
Repository class for managing CalendarEntry entities.

This class implements the ICalendarEntryRepository interface and provides methods to perform CRUD operations on CalendarEntry entities using a data access object (DAO).
